opam remove ocamlfind
brew uninstall opam
brew uninstall ocaml
install opam from sh
remove .opam directory
opam init --comp 4.00.1

Directories where OCaml will be installed:
        binaries.................. /Users/chuajiesheng/.opam/4.00.1/bin
        standard library.......... /Users/chuajiesheng/.opam/4.00.1/lib/ocaml
        manual pages.............. /Users/chuajiesheng/.opam/4.00.1/man (with extension .1)

eval `opam config env`
opam install ocamlfind

